{"tid":1745994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家對呢場抗爭有咩目標？","createTime":"2019-11-22T13:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T16:04:13.000Z","uid":162783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"338b9f08de1f8108a5b1d769e6d8f5693be32bf5","tid":1745994,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:45:35.000Z","msg":"對我黎講，就係要<span style=\"color: red;\">將香港人身份+追求自由既意志繼承落去。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中共既目的就係要滅絕我地年青一代</span>，只要我地死哂，就冇人會敢為自由發聲。敢怒而不敢言，被人打壓既情況就會更加嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n廢老繼續廢落去，細路仔接受洗腦式教育，而後<span style=\"color: red;\">生仔族群就會被大陸人取代</span>，黎個大換血。之後香港就會好自然咁完全變成中國都冇人理。港共買大陸tg，放成萬粒就知咩事，就係要毒害我地後代，生育率下降，之後就放哂大陸人落黎生活，建立全新既共港。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">縱使身死，但心不死</span>，我地要將思想傳落去，堅持理念，感染全世界所有人(包括藍絲，雖然好難)。梁天琦講過最重要係堅持，同埋要有盼望，只要大家都有共同信念，就會凝聚一股神秘力量！<br />\n<br />\n所以，都係個句，<span style=\"color: red;\">be water，不被捕！</span><br />\n<br />\n請大家以後每個行動，都要思考一下後果，諗多幾個plan，點樣減少受傷避免被捕。你冇對等既武器，一定唔會打得贏。<span style=\"color: red;\">暴力係解決問題最有效率既方法，但前提係要有絕對壓倒性既力量。</span><br />\n<br />\n勇武一定要<span style=\"color: red;\">be water</span>，因為你地，幫大家爭取到更多表達訴求既空間同時間，所以冇左你地唔得！！出去抗爭，要集中精神，部分和理非唔好再掛住打卡玩手機，<span style=\"color: red;\">要時刻保持危機意識</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地要為死左既手足戰鬥落去，一直思考，直至搵到為佢地尋冤得雪既方法，我地唔可以再有人犧牲了，加油！</span>"},{"pid":"293f871d94ebb7442423b505efdb66461e047a75","tid":1745994,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:46:10.000Z","msg":"戰役過後，痛定思痛，認清現實，重新出發(抗爭五部曲-前言)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742018</a>"},{"pid":"213945a30df3e776b3ac93cdfb943974ca882895","tid":1745994,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"293f871d94ebb7442423b505efdb66461e047a75","tid":1745994,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:46:10.000Z","msg":"戰役過後，痛定思痛，認清現實，重新出發(抗爭五部曲-前言)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742018</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:56:06.000Z","msg":"共勉之"},{"pid":"ba70a8c5711348f1732504d4da01dcf6a690434a","tid":1745994,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cac692ace31062cd07730f2589a6e85899dc689","tid":1745994,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:41:04.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"40fdee30b6e74e7c4617600e94856142ef33a638","tid":1745994,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:14:14.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"598faa6dd3714da8ed19e6c234c3ed5cfeeb3612","tid":1745994,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:14:32.000Z","msg":"4／10"},{"pid":"e882e9e087f1c0852189d25c6c33d737c11f7a4b","tid":1745994,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:14:43.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"d2db15c361d6752c27afd3c1340f7d1d75e195fb","tid":1745994,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:14:53.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"3e0fd682123b9f808b909daaaada26c90d4bd872","tid":1745994,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"3e033a652b02fd24325abb8ca45e4d9696aa5e6e","tid":1745994,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:15:17.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"fb713857e570afe4481b38058f40df1fcd3b6179","tid":1745994,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:15:27.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"2c365f9cd8f6a9b22d31d3d191271812a056c235","tid":1745994,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:15:48.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"5b8afa42344283005b5ec27f3032333b4ccaeb56","tid":1745